"trong khung hình."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:878
msgid ""
"The Object Detector effect employs machine learning algorithms (such as "
"neural networks) to identify and highlight objects within the video frame. "
"It can recognize multiple object types, such as vehicles, people, animals, "
"and more! This can be used for analytical purposes, to add interactive "
"elements to videos, or to track the movement of specific objects across the "
"frame."
msgstr ""
